- Use https, not http api. (Evan McClain)
- Fix incorrect pluralising of relative time. (Deskin Miller)
- Fixed #1998551, the double-escaping of < and >. (Mike Lundy)
- Fixed #1961611, character count behavior. (Brian Pepple)

